90d9b631-9b41-4001-828e-1985e81f3b96.title: Ted Rehnison
90d9b631-9b41-4001-828e-1985e81f3b96.text: Go away. We don't want any.

19bae0ee-ab74-4c3b-9ac9-4a3ea95c4413.title: Note
19bae0ee-ab74-4c3b-9ac9-4a3ea95c4413.text: Do you have the book Jethick gave you?

7e2e5fbf-4741-4177-96e0-9e91290083b4.title: Ted Rehnison
7e2e5fbf-4741-4177-96e0-9e91290083b4.text: Go away. We don't want any.

6400fb49-5d3e-4367-89c2-5df16dd9676b.title: <player>
6400fb49-5d3e-4367-89c2-5df16dd9676b.text:
I'm a friend of Jethick's, I have come to return a book
he borrowed.

f9e958b3-d40b-4785-825f-fd9c6556f799.title: Ted Rehnison
f9e958b3-d40b-4785-825f-fd9c6556f799.text: Oh... Why didn't you say, come in then.

e1d14ec6-ed37-483b-90c9-580909ef4d19.text: You hand the book to Ted as you enter.

6f6526e0-261e-436e-8d50-aca5f75c07af.text:
You need to have the book to
give to Ted.

1485cdb4-eccf-4806-99e1-3873a8fdb619.title: Note
1485cdb4-eccf-4806-99e1-3873a8fdb619.text:
Allow access to the 
Rehnison's house.

2d22e042-217e-4864-a1d4-9972bf89c649.title: <player>
2d22e042-217e-4864-a1d4-9972bf89c649.text: Hi, I hear a woman called Elena is staying here.

c3eec999-c89c-48df-8057-303eab2b9499.title: Ted Rehnison
c3eec999-c89c-48df-8057-303eab2b9499.text:
Yes she was staying here, but slightly over a week ago
she was getting ready to go back. However she never
managed to leave.

dffcda0b-8274-481f-b679-e6ed46f5bc03.title: Ted Rehnison
dffcda0b-8274-481f-b679-e6ed46f5bc03.text:
My daughter Milli was playing near the west wall when
she saw some shadowy figures jump out and grab her.
Milli is upstairs if you wish to speak to her.

cf86b7e0-85df-443a-a720-cce6d5e20228.title: Ted Rehnison
cf86b7e0-85df-443a-a720-cce6d5e20228.text: I wish you luck, she did a lot for us.

9af089bf-af11-49b4-b3cb-20f6e0afc60c.title: <player>
9af089bf-af11-49b4-b3cb-20f6e0afc60c.text: Yes, she is safe at home now.

fb9e7636-bf98-42bc-8f7e-9c24c69b55a7.title: Ted Rehnison
fb9e7636-bf98-42bc-8f7e-9c24c69b55a7.text: That's good to hear, she helped us a lot.
